:0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC 八大</span>以外：</span><br />\n<br />\n- 1989 年：<ins>香港公開進修學院 Open Learning Institute of Hong Kong</ins> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/U3kWDt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FU3kWDt&h=54b4187c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1996 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">OUHK 香港公開大學 (The Open University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/927kLE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F927kLE&h=cd63fa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n- 1971 年：<ins>香港樹仁書院</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1976 年：<ins>香港樹仁學院 Hong Kong Shun Yan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/dMuwSp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdMuwSp&h=b9cb712f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2006 年</span></span>：正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKSYU 香港樹仁大學 (Hong Kong Shue Yan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/sTVBnU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsTVBnU&h=7621e2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/8HdgNc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8HdgNc&h=7deef38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n補充資料 2：<br />\n香港其實有二十大（如果計 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">QF level 5 degree-issuing</span></span>）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fedu-sy