quote><br />\n<br />\n岩呀<br />\n所以ive咪贏囉<br />\n<br />\n砌車呢類技術係管理層既專長定係唔使點讀書既工人既專長先？<br />\n<br />\nIve就係量產堆工人出黎被人管，<br />\n連工人技術都輸比管理層真係可以番屋企訓</blockquote>唔同意，依家係同major嘅人去鬥自己專業範疇入邊嘅嘢喎，<span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係人哋外國名校Management major人去鬥ive啲engineer喎。</span>你估名校就一定係得Management major冇Engineering<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得呢壇嘢抵讚喎，點解唔可以去acknowledge下人哋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你未訓醒，我無講過唔係外國engine major<br />\nCambridge 咩major都係番黎管人<br />\n<br />\n同樣道理ive開management hd都係出黎負責被人管<br />\n<br />\n仲有我無唔acknowledge人地既effort，<br />\n當然要讚佢地係做技工技能上做得出色，方便被cambridge既人管理"},{"pid":"017031208b2d8afd76b6a53181f59088d407612e","tid":604334,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真係乜都唔識架喎<br />\n你估放幾塊 solar cell 就有電郁咩，入面 converter circuit，energy management 唔洗設計既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我話你知，工程就係讀呢啲野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>同埋個比賽應該點玩，計分條式點樣分析，應該幾時用後備電爆速度，幾時用 solar cell 餵電拎 efficiency 分數，呢啲都要用數學工具分析 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大佬我識計PID aerodynamic 又要匯報上黎你知咩<br />\n我教人solidwork又要講？讀pde sde又要利申？<br />\n使唔使我學black schole又要報告埋上黎？<br />\n<br />\n大佬ive hd大電學埋fourier transform添<br />\n咁點呢？咪去左做維修學徒囉</blockquote>IVE 就係係你提及既知識上面，贏左大部分外國名校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以點解ive係狗cambridge管狗<br />\nIve仲打飛機吹自己識幾多既時候<br />\nCambridge 已經學埋政商法同去識人</blockquote>咪右係做狗</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n管狗呢個工作都做到成隻狗咁"},{"pid":"75998d82efbe0b26e04dd20d4c435836fb860d2b","tid":604334,"uid":175719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b197d60829eeaa4342df3bb52fcc206dddae30a6","tid":604334,"uid":175719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"